`` Alejandro '' is a song by American singer Lady Gaga .
Musically , it is a mid-tempo synthpop song .
Gaga performed the song on the ninth season of American Idol and has performed it on all dates of The Monster Ball Tour .
The song charted in the United Kingdom and Hungary due to digital sales following the album 's release .
